<h2>Questions</h2>
<div class='field-container'>
<h3><label for="application_questions_0_0">Links</label></h3>
<div class='directions'>
<p>Please include any that you have: GitHub, LinkedIn, personal web site, etc.</p>
</div>
<textarea data-validate="notEmpty" id="application_questions_0_0" maxlength="" name="application[questions][0][0]">
</textarea>
<div class='question error'>Please enter your GitHub, LinkedIn and other URLs.</div>
</div>
<div class='field-container'>
<h3><label for="application_questions_0_1">Code CracklePop</label></h3>
<div class='directions'>
<p><p>Write a program that prints out the numbers 1 to 100 (inclusive). If the number is divisible by 3, print <em>Crackle</em> instead of the number. If it's divisible by 5, print <em>Pop</em>. If it's divisible by both 3 and 5, print <em>CracklePop</em>. You can use any language.</p></p>
</div>
<textarea data-validate="notEmpty" id="application_questions_0_1" maxlength="" name="application[questions][0][1]">
</textarea>
<div class='question error'>Please solve CracklePop</div>
</div>
<div class='field-container'>
<h3><label for="application_questions_0_2">Please link to a program you&#39;ve written from scratch.</label></h3>
<div class='directions'>
<p>You can use something like <a href="https://gist.github.com/">GitHub's gist</a> to host your code.  It doesn't need to be long, but it should be something you've written yourself, and not using a framework (e.g., Rails).  If you don't have anything to submit, code something small, like a game of tic-tac-toe.</p>
</div>
<textarea data-validate="notEmpty" id="application_questions_0_2" maxlength="" name="application[questions][0][2]">
</textarea>
<div class='question error'>Please share a program you've written.</div>
</div>
<div class='field-container'>
<h3><label for="application_questions_0_3">What is the most fascinating thing you&#39;ve learned in the past month?</label></h3>
<div class='directions'>
<p>This doesn't have to be about programming.</p>
</div>
<textarea data-validate="notEmpty" id="application_questions_0_3" maxlength="1500" name="application[questions][0][3]">
</textarea>
<div class='question error'>Please share a fascinating thing you've learned recently.</div>
</div>
<div class='field-container'>
<h3><label for="application_questions_0_4">What do you want to be doing in two years?</label></h3>
<textarea data-validate="notEmpty" id="application_questions_0_4" maxlength="1500" name="application[questions][0][4]">
</textarea>
<div class='question error'>Please tell us what you'd like to be doing in two years. It's ok to say, &quot;I don't know.&quot;</div>
</div>
<div class='field-container'>
<h3><label for="application_questions_0_5">Why do you want to do Hacker School?</label></h3>
<textarea data-validate="notEmpty" id="application_questions_0_5" maxlength="1500" name="application[questions][0][5]">
</textarea>
